Meson building
--------------

1.  Copy / make a meson_options.txt. The look to see 
    if theres an existing meson_options.txt for you platform.
    The defaults in each should be decent for most systems

2.  Modify the meson_options.txt to use the backends you want.


3.  Run the following to build the defaults:

  meson output
  cd ./output
  meson compile
